defaultproposals to change legal aid will have a devastating impact on prisoners’ access to justice. The justifications for the changes include grossly misleading characterisations as to why prisoners seek legal assistance (to get an ‘easier ride’). In reality th
defaulte proposals will mean that prisoners will not be able to seek legally aided advic
defaulte on issues such as segregation, 
defaultaccess to mother and baby units
