defaulte was granted Release on Temporary Licence (ROTL) to attend an NA meeting in the community, he travelled unaccompanied and returned to the prison at 11pm as per the licence.  If there were genuine concerns regarding his health, a ROTL surely would not have
default been granted in his case.  
